{"tid":1206226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[RTHK]聖約瑟書院宣佈中一及中三考試延期  HKT 09:59","createTime":"2019-06-12T02:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T02:06:25.000Z","uid":103207,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee16bcc5c1d6ff72968f7d75cda453aad0b3cfdb","tid":1206226,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:03:12.000Z","msg":"2019-06-12 HKT 09:59<br />\n分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n立法會今日恢復二讀修訂《逃犯條例》草案，大批示威者早上突然衝出龍和道，佔據了馬路，夏慤道亦被示威者佔據，現場交通嚴重受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">位於中環堅尼地道的聖約瑟書院，在學校網頁宣佈，原定今日舉行的中一英文科及中三數學科考試將會延期，校方又建議學生為安全計，暫時留在家中。</span><br />\n<br />\n學校職員接受本台查詢時表示，由於各級考試時間有別，中二、中四及中五級別的學生，今日需繼續回校。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462262-20190612.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462262-20190612.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J4D442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=d2929f2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462262-20190612.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=14543e8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462262-20190612.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f5913763468071174ccc2528fc8cdc8159d4cd85","tid":1206226,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:06:25.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing Singing a song of angry men!!!!"}]}